      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental dataset must include at least three independent replicates per operating point to enable statistical characterization of experimental variability.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark dataset includes five independent experimental replicates per operating point conducted across two laboratories. Coefficient of variation for measured HI ranges from 8% to 19% across operating points, providing adequate statistical characterization of experimental variability. Test samples criterion met at level 2."
    },
